I've found an issue in using GET instead of POST.  The querystring variables are not getting URLEncoded and and error is thrown if the value has a string in it.  I've fixed this by replacing this line:

String paramString = p.getName() + "=" + p.getValue();

With this:

String paramString = p.getName() + "=" + URLEncoder.encode(p.getValue(),"UTF-8");

